        Nulla facilisi. Sed iaculis blandit quam. Nunc scelerisque ligula eget lectus consectetur faucibus. Maecenas sit amet laoreet justo. Maecenas nulla massa, vestibulum id laoreet at, condimentum sit amet sapien. Suspendisse potenti. Fusce posuere elementum est, sit amet facilisis nulla tempus quis. Aenean volutpat orci quis blandit dignissim. Nunc augue turpis, ultricies id ante non, auctor mattis eros. Mauris rutrum odio a augue tempus tincidunt. Phasellus fringilla ultrices enim sit amet viverra.
    </p>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>ID</th>
                <th>Nama Pegawai</th>
                <th>Jabatan</th>
                <th>Departemen</th>
                <th>Tanggal Bergabung</th>
                <th>Gaji</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            @foreach (var item in Model)
            {
                <tr>
                    <td>@item.Id</td>
                    <td>@item.Name</td>
                    <td>@item.Position</td>
                    <td>@item.Department</td>
                    <td class="date">@item.JoinDate.ToString("dd/MM/yyyy")</td>
                    <td class="currency">@string.Format("{0:N0}", item.Salary)</td>
                </tr>
            }
        </tbody>
    </table>
</body>
</html>